<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>输液时间计算器</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>输液时间计算器</h1>
<p>本计算器可以帮助你计算两阶段输液所需的时间。</p>

<form>
阶段1:<br>
<label>输液量(毫升): <input type="number" id="volume1"></label><br>  
<label>每分钟滴数: <input type="number" id="drop_rate1"></label><br>
<label>点滴系数: <input type="number" step="0.1" id="drop_factor1"></label><br>

阶段2:<br> 
<label>输液量(毫升): <input type="number" id="volume2"></label><br>
<label>每分钟滴数: <input type="number" id="drop_rate2"></label><br>
<label>点滴系数: <input type="number" step="0.1" id="drop_factor2"></label><br>

<button type="button" onclick="calculate()">计算时间</button>
</form>

<div id="result"></div>

<script>
function calculate() {
  let volume1 = document.getElementById("volume1").value; 
  let drop_rate1 = document.getElementById("drop_rate1").value;
  let drop_factor1 = document.getElementById("drop_factor1").value;
  let time1 = volume1 * drop_factor1 * 60 / drop_rate1;
  
  let volume2 = document.getElementById("volume2").value;
  let drop_rate2 = document.getElementById("drop_rate2").value;
  let drop_factor2 = document.getElementById("drop_factor2").value;
  let time2 = volume2 * drop_factor2 * 60 / drop_rate2;
  
  document.getElementById("result").innerHTML = "阶段1所需时间:" + time1 + " 分钟<br>阶段2所需时间:" + time2 + " 分钟";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
